"As discussed yesterday, regarding point 1 that the customer raised:

Per my investigation with the vendor, our ECDS inquiry system indeed has a '票面下载' (Bill Face Download) function. When this button is clicked, it allows for the download of selected Bills of Exchange (BADs). However, we've found that only signed BADs allow for the download of both the '票据正面' (front of the bill) and '票据背面' (back of the bill). For unsigned BADs, only the '票据正面' can be downloaded.

This difference in logic when clicking the same button is quite inappropriate and could lead to confusion."
